Package: medstats
Title: Medical Statistics Toolkit for Clinical Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("陕嘉宇", email = "user@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for medical statistics, providing streamlined functions for
    baseline tables, regression analysis (GLM, Cox), GEE repeated measures, and publication-ready
    plots (KM curves, forest plots, RCS splines, ROC curves, Sankey diagrams, line/bar charts).
    Also includes utilities for formatting flextable objects and exporting tables to Word documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
